{"tid":155910,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Ryzen 7 1800X / 1700X 溫度偏高? 其實是AMD加的偏移","createTime":"2017-03-14T11:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T01:35:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a9b7d07c4ed0be1809893a2d8dabc1241c9323","tid":155910,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Ryzen 7 1800X / 1700X 溫度偏高? 其實是AMD加的偏移<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coolaler.com/threads/ryzen-7-1800x-1700x-amd.343083/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fryzen-7-1800x-1700x-amd.343083%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRehv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4c6bd614\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coolaler.com/threads/ryzen-7-1800x-1700x-amd.343083/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\nAMD Ryzen 1800X / 1700X 測試時待機溫度偏高，有很多網友表示懷疑，說真的實測的人大多使用了 AMD 自家新的超頻監控軟體，你說他不準，連我自己都質疑了，尤其是與 Ryzen 1700 相比，1800X、1700X 明顯高出許多，本來以為是BIOS的問題，結果是 AMD 自行加上去的偏移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/msi/x370_xpower_gaming_titanium/81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fmsi%2Fx370_xpower_gaming_titanium%2F81.jpg&h=721a6dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母板 BIOS 內與 AMD 的官方超頻工具 Ryzen Master 是可以看得到 Ryzen 處理器的內核溫度的，然而 AMD 今天放出了一份公告說這個溫度也是不準確的，<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單來說 AMD Ryzen 處理器的主要溫度傳感器 tCTL 在 Ryzen 7 1800X 與 Ryzen 7 1700X 上設置了+20℃的偏移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>，這樣做的目的是為了確保所有 Ryzen 處理器都有一致的風扇策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說你們現在看到 Ryzen 7 處理器的溫度偏高是個假象，實際溫度需要減去20℃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，AMD 相信溫度檢測軟體很快就會更新修正這個偏移，正確的報告實時溫度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/17/03/Ryzen_temp_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F17%2F03%2FRyzen_temp_2.jpg&h=a27372a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修正這個似乎不是很難啊，但是確保風扇保有一致規則卻去+20℃這種做法似乎也太戇鳩，即使使用這做法，也可以讓顯示的溫度回歸到正常才對。"},{"pid":"054cea05c7de3bc884b32c03edd879923f0ed30b","tid":155910,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"點解1700唔洗+20&deg;c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2d5c497216f2c5b318672d36bb27e2e6571563","tid":155910,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解1700唔洗+20&deg;c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1800X 1700X熱得快啲所以要+20度等佢早啲開風扇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0e69df9c1510d840f040bd89ef9a3fff30397e","tid":155910,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38440980de8bbde013aea50ca14f03015a6a2b2","tid":155910,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔明點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就信唔過自己d cpu 要做高個溫度嚇鳩人"},{"pid":"404ad147c9dd9b7a898ab975a3fd4782ea65e431","tid":155910,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"有玩開oc既一睇就覺得戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db56154e34f8c1302330870c1fb0981665b34259","tid":155910,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5604bf92e08a8e300744cf07a7f265d9cfdab411","tid":155910,"uid":60009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T01:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔明點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就信唔過自己d cpu 要做高個溫度嚇鳩人</blockquote><br />\n佢係信唔過人哋啲散熱器啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255811fd4ea77ccb2d4360cb2e1f28dc64aa6067","tid":155910,"uid":90108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔明點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就信唔過自己d cpu 要做高個溫度嚇鳩人</blockquote><br />\n佢係信唔過人哋啲散熱器啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/psqxebur\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpsqxebur&h=e361f996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試緊電壓果陣嘅溫度 實際4ghz full load 得70度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bf83979d119dd9f91afd2a1dca950f294cc0b7","tid":155910,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}